OL,3,C'I'm in fear for my family's life'
OL,5,FThe moment Lenny Scott told police he
OL,6,Fbelieved his family home was being
OL,7,Fwatched has been played to the jury in
OL,8,Fthe trial over his murder. Elias
OL,9,FMorgan and Anthony Cleary are accused
OL,10,Fof the murder of Mr Scott, who was
OL,11,Ffatally injured when he was shot on
OL,12,FPeel Road in Skelmersdale on February
OL,13,F8 last year.
OL,15,FAlex Leach KC, prosecuting, has told
OL,16,Fthe jury at Preston Crown Court that
OL,17,Fprison officer and dad-of-three Mr
OL,18,FScott had been "murdered as an act of
OL,19,Fretaliation" after he exposed an
OL,20,Fillicit relationship between convict
OL,21,FMorgan and one of his colleagues.
