OL,3,C'I'm in fear for my family's life'
OL,5,FThe 13-person jury, of nine men and
OL,6,Ffour women, heard that after failing
OL,7,Fto convince Mr Scott not to report a
OL,8,Fphone containing evidence of the
OL,9,Frelationship to his superiors, Morgan
OL,10,Fallegedly told him: "I'll bide my
OL,11,Ftime, but I promise I will get you"
OL,12,Fbefore allegedly making a gun gesture.
OL,14,FOn the third day of the trial,
OL,15,FThursday, June 26, the jury heard a
OL,16,Fphone call made by Mr Scott to 101
OL,17,Fjust days after he had seized the
OL,18,FiPhone from Morgan on March 26, 2020.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
