OL,3,C'I'm in fear for my family's life'
OL,5,FSpeaking to the call operator, the
OL,6,Fprison officer for HMP Altcourse tells
OL,7,Fher he was in fear of his family's
OL,8,Fsafety after Morgan allegedly had men
OL,9,Fwatching his house.
OL,11,FWhen asked who was making the threat
OL,12,Fon Mr Scott and his family, he said:
OL,13,F"Elias Morgan. He's described my
OL,14,Ffamily, to a tee, and my house. He
OL,15,Fsaid he's had them (men) there just
OL,16,Fready.
