OL,3,C'I'm in fear for my family's life'
OL,5,FThe dad continued: "He said he's got
OL,6,Flads everywhere. He's described my
OL,7,Fvehicle and he's described my house
OL,8,Fand what my girlfriend and twin boys
OL,9,Flook like."
OL,11,FWhen asked whether Morgan was
OL,12,F"chatting over this", Mr Scott replied
OL,13,FMorgan was "being too specific" for it
OL,14,Fnot to be true. "I've got twins,
OL,15,Fthey're twins but they have different
OL,16,Fcoloured hair," he told the operator.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
