OL,3,C'I'm in fear for my family's life'
OL,5,F"He's got everything to a tee. He's
OL,6,Fdescribed my house, everything. This
OL,7,Fis my third jail, I've been threatened
OL,8,Fall the time but this is closer to
OL,9,Fhome."
OL,11,FDue to the incident happening at the
OL,12,Fbeginning of the Covid-19 pandemic, Mr
OL,13,FScott explained how his girlfriend,
OL,14,FLucy Griffiths, and children were self-
OL,15,Fisolating before apologising to the
OL,16,Foperator. He said: "I'm sorry if you
OL,17,Fthink I'm wasting your time."
