OL,5,FThe call continues as the operator
OL,6,Farranges for a patrol car to meet him
OL,7,Fnear his house by the time he leaves
OL,8,Fthe prison and gets home.
OL,10,FAnalysis of the phone "revealed Elias
OL,11,FMorgan was engaged in a sexual
OL,12,Frelationship with another prison
OL,13,Fofficer, Sarah Williams" the court
OL,14,Fheard. Mr Leach added: "It was clear
OL,15,Fthat she had provided Elias Morgan
OL,16,Fwith details about other prisoners.
OL,17,FThe court heard Mr Scott gave a
OL,18,Fwitness statement and Morgan was
OL,19,Farrested and interviewed under caution.
