OL,3,C'I'm in fear for my family's life'
OL,5,FWilliams admitted three offences of
OL,6,Fmisconduct in a public officer and a
OL,7,Fcomputer misuse offence, while Morgan
OL,8,Fpleaded not guilty to unauthorised
OL,9,Fpossession of the mobile phone. His
OL,10,Ftrial was adjourned until February 19
OL,11,F2024 - 11 days after Mr Scott was
OL,12,Fkilled.
OL,14,FMorgan, 35, of Highgate Street, and
OL,15,FCleary, 29, of Smithdown Lane, both
OL,16,Fdeny murder. Cleary also denies a
OL,17,Fsecond count of manslaughter. The
OL,18,Ftrial before Mr Justice Goose
OL,19,Fcontinues.
